  "text": "Gold nanoparticles coated with indolicidin against Candida biofilms attachment or within the biofilms. [CITATION_1] Furthermore, the use of NPs as carriers allows drug efficacy to be enhanced by overcoming resistance mechanisms, such as degradation of β-lactamase, efflux pumps, or wide cell walls. [CITATION_2] In this work, we have provided sound evidence that the AuNPs-indolicidin complex can easily penetrate the biofilm matrix and the cells, altering fungal membrane permeability as well as reducing the cell population.",
